g src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63c22b6aa7b36ba74967c414f44ca965f812d86f","tid":1740903,"uid":46151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"61ede73219b0c4c530e6e2e8e5bcb2f8848ca3e2","tid":1740903,"uid":56424,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T08:27:47.000Z","msg":"AMD/INTEL 玩緊7nm, 你玩16nm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T09:25:42.000Z","msg":"intel咪又係14+++++++++++++++<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa7972f3ebe7b6afea827bfd45a70008579944c1","tid":1740903,"uid":1751,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"f2e6216881fb75bacceab063213187983a93abd5","tid":1740903,"uid":15406,"like":173,"dislike":2,"score":171,"quote":{"pid":"d316b56f974feb8f24b6f426c22463a917eb5eda","tid":1740903,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T06:07:26.000Z","msg":"【性能達 Zen2 水平?!】支援 DDR5、 PCIe 4.0<br />\n國產兆芯 KX-7000 要追上 AMD、Intel 了!!<br />\n<br />\n儘管 X86 處理器是 Intel 的私有指令集，不過國內依然通過各種方式獲得了合法 X86 授權，其中上海兆芯通過 VIA 合資獲得了 X86 授權，並且從 KX-5000 系列開始走上了自研架構的道路，<span style=\"color: red;\">日前新一代的 KX-6000 處理器正式發佈了，最多 8 核心、時脈 3.0GHz，官方表示性能比 Intel 的七代 Core i5-7400 處理器更強</span>。<br />\n<br />\n上海兆芯是 VIA 威盛與上海政府基金成立的合資公司，獲得了 X86 授權，在 2017 到 2018 年間展示的處理器主要是 KX-5000 系列，代號&ldquo;wudaokou&rdquo;（五道口），採用 28nm 工藝，時脈 2.2GHz，I/O 方面支援 PCIe 3.0/USB 3.1 Gen2（Type-C ）等，號稱代碼 100% 自有，設計絕無第三方參與。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zYqvvvp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzYqvvvp.png&h=e3a263ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iDKDEoK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiDKDEoK.png&h=df42122b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在今年 6 月份，兆芯正式發佈了接替 KX-5000 系列的全新 KX-6000 處理器，升級到了 16nm 工藝，時脈提升到 3GHz，有 4 核心及 8 核心兩種規格，還支援 PCIe 4.0、雙通道 DDR4-3200 記憶體，搭配的晶片組升級到了 KH-3000 系列。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">兆芯 KX-6000 系列處理器此前已經多次展示過，官方曾表示 KX-6000 系列產品在性能跑分方面已經和 Intel 的第七代桌面 i5 處理器相當。至於規劃中的 KX-7000 則基於完全煥然一新的微架構，採用 7nm 工藝，不僅支援 DDR5，還將演進到 PCIe 4.0 總線，而兆芯總工王惟林稱 KX-7000 的性能目標是「<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">將達到同期 AMD 的水平</span>」，對標的 CPU 至少是 Zen2 級別</span>。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oZBbeYi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoZBbeYi.png&h=33c45351&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T06:16:52.000Z","msg":"圖二用緊老翻windows<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T09:29:53.000Z","msg":"你的windows 不是正版"},{"pid":"31616d4d646d042e02eafb7db5db063bde8c6355","tid":1740903,"uid":3076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T09:33:24.000Z","msg":"買到機整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"542a6efea91bd99266ce63493eaeb8e5b6267a00","tid":1740903,"uid":216750,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T09:37:09.000Z","msg":"好嘢，又成功搵間諜偷左技術。<br />\n可惜丫，中國永遠只靠偷，都冇可能發展到另一種技術。因為共狗只不過錢比其他人多，智慧比一般人低"},{"pid":"e35f4f3a4fdcef32e8dfbe2a7630596b23a4edb7","tid":1740903,"uid":10733,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T09:40:37.000Z","msg":"買番粒試下咪清楚<br />\n邊度有得買？"},{"pid":"db23b44e579a964061df13b3e75fa80d40b4ce3b","tid":1740903,"uid":321339,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T09:43:26.000Z","msg":"國產CPU咁勁，點解之前中興畀美國搞到要休業<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a41186819053356751308b7f386e9dec1b18303d","tid":1740903,"uid":5601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT